{"tid":2131873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[納綷黨成立一百年系列]  當他們逮捕一班極少數妨害国家安全嘅人","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T08:50:47.000Z","uid":151074,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79e88b688a571014ac7fdf0ac2b23c64591f03aa","tid":2131873,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"當他們將陳淑莊、黃之鋒的著作下架的時候<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n我又不是睇陳淑莊、黃之鋒啲書嗰班人<br />\n<br />\n當他們逮捕泛民班人的時候<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n我又不是支持泛民班人<br />\n<br />\n當他們批鬥教育界的時候<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n我又不是老師<br />\n<br />\n當他們批鬥公務員的時候<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n我又不是公務員<br />\n<br />\n當他們準備DQ立法會候選人的時候<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n我又不是要選立法會<br />\n<br />\n當他們逮捕學生動源的時候<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n我又不是學生動源的人<br />\n<br />\n當他們逮捕我的時候<br />\n已經沒有人能為我說話了<br />\n<br />\n1920年2月24日，國家社會主義德國工人黨(納綷黨)成立"},{"pid":"50e0f15018ad414d8bc98494f1d443192f4eff10","tid":2131873,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vO-_HXO7HwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvO-_HXO7HwY&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhEn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=5d4ed44c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vO-_HXO7HwY</a>"},{"pid":"80f1cf05629b5a34f221aa39ebdbc29d0739ad27","tid":2131873,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e576eeaba169fb8fecf709103ea3c75d6a9c933c","tid":2131873,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed8867da58d666ec8f348f545e6256016226b268","tid":2131873,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a854f35a469bbef4a40ea6aa933b4a51866733","tid":2131873,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e576eeaba169fb8fecf709103ea3c75d6a9c933c","tid":2131873,"uid":